bacillus Calmette-Guerin scar formation and tuberculin skin test
reactivity in infants in Lima, Peru. Pediatrics. 2003; 112(4): e298.
Available at
http://pediatrics.aappublications.org/content/112/4/e298.long.
3. Chan PC, Chang LY, Wu YC, et al: Age-specific cut-offs for the
