children. Int J Tuberc Lung Dis. 2008; 12(12): 1401-6. Available at
http://docstore.ingenta.com/cgi-bin/ds_deliver/1/u/d/ISIS/63724459.1/iuatld/ijtld/2008/00000012/00000012/art00012/005ED3EEC7920A1C1311696632AFC7D0F75E0BAEDB.pdf
